mple of equality and respect is the team welcome ceremony.\", \"from\": 2877, \"to\": 2978, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2892, \"end\": 2907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.720871313045902e-24, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another example\", \"from\": 2909, \"to\": 2924}, {\"ngram\": \"equality\", \"from\": 2928, \"to\": 2936}, {\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 2941, \"to\": 2948}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 2952, \"to\": 2960}, {\"ngram\": \"ceremony\", \"from\": 2969, \"to\": 2977}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every delegation \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 big or small \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 enjoys this short but meaningful ritual: A welcome message from the village mayor to mark the official arrival of the teams in the village, the playing of the national anthem and the raising of the national flag, an exchange of souvenirs and a photo op between the village mayor and the head of each delegation.\", \"from\": 2979, \"to\": 3328, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Every delegation\", \"from\": 2979, \"to\": 2995}, {\"ngram\": \"big or small \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093\", \"from\": 3000, \"to\": 3016}, {\"ngram\": \"the village mayor\", \"from\": 3081, \"to\": 3098}, {\"ngram\": \"the official arrival\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3127}, {\"ngram\": \"the teams\", \"from\": 3131, \"to\": 3140}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 3144, \"to\": 3155}, {\"ngram\": \"the playing\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3168}, {\"ngram\": \"the national anthem\", \"from\": 3172, \"to\": 3191}, {\"ngram\": \"the raising\", \"from\": 3196, \"to\": 3207}, {\"ngram\": \"the national flag\", \"from\": 3211, \"to\": 3228}, {\"ngram\": \"an exchange\", \"from\": 3230, \"to\": 3241}, {\"ngram\": \"souvenirs\", \"from\": 3245, \"to\": 3254}, {\"ngram\": \"a photo o